body:
I’m starting one, because why not! Join if you’re a dan and phil fan who’s looking for friends

description: this is an 18+ chat although there is no age restriction on it. i won’t stop minors from joining, but don’t complain about stuff being inappropriate for your age, kay? also, there are no trigger warnings in this server. this is a say whatever you want chat, if you’re easily triggered or offended, don’t join lmao and if you do and complain later, i won’t have it!

just a nice friendly open for all ages chat. basic rules of healthy social conduct apply. no further restrictions. bring out your inner demon! whether you ship phan or not, whether you write fics, draw art, post shitty memes, looking for everlasting friendships, or do nothing with your life… all are welcome!


just be reasonable kay? the best version of yourself :P

summary:
I have a conspiracy theory that Phil accidentally killed Dan. 
Considering the fact that he recently almost set a fire because...
body:
I have a conspiracy theory that Phil accidentally killed Dan.

Considering the fact that he recently almost set a fire because of a pizza it’s not impossible that something else happened before that.

It would also explain the ads about funerals and cremation because of course he would be googling that.

And from time to time he just goes on Dan’s twitter and posts an existential tweet so we won’t get suspicious and that’s why we haven’t seen Dan’s face for so long and why the gaming channel isn’t back. Thanks for coming to my ted talk.

summary: He looks at me with his wonderous eyes then laughs as he takes a sip of his wine.“funny that you have the courage to come to me...
body:
He looks at me with his wonderous eyes then laughs as he takes a sip of his wine.“funny that you have the courage to come to me knowing you don’t even have a single coin to buy anything from my shop.”

I sniffle but stare up at him timidly my eyes nearly wailing up With tears

“it’s only because i spent it all here mr.Lester!”

“as you should.” he would then quickly state i bite my lip then drop to my knees.

  “p-please! i beg of you give me time to earn money so i can buy your merch before it’s sold out!” I’d cry nearly clingy to his leg now.

He would then place his wine down and taps his chin thoughtfully  laughing shortly  after while  proceeding to look down on me with a  judgemental stare.

“well. It sucks to be you now doesn’t it?”
